quote_first: I pulled into the Aoyama supermarket parking garage at
quote_last: . The sky to the east was getting light. I entered the store carrying my bag. Almost no one was in the place. A young clerk in a striped uniform sat reading a magazine; a woman of indeterminate age was buying a cartload of cans and instant food. I turned past the liquor display and went straight to the snack bar.
title: Hard Boiled Wonderland and the End of the World
author: Haruki Murakami
